	<datafield ind1="1" ind2=" " tag="505">
		<subfield code="6">880-08</subfield>
		<subfield code="a">al-Juzʼ al-awwal. Yaḥtawī ʻalá tārīkh ādāb al-lughah al-ʻArabīyah fī ʻaṣr al-Jāhilīyah wa- ʻaṣr al-Rāshidīn wa-al-ʻaṣr al-Umawī ay min aqdam azminat al-tārīkh ilá sanat 132 H -- al-Juzʼ al-thānī. Yaḥtawī ʻalá tārīkh ādāb al-lughah al-ʻArabīyah fī al-ʻaṣr al-ʻAbbāsī min qiyām al-dawlah al-ʻAbbāsīyah sanat 132 H. ilá dukhūl al-Salājiqah Baghdād sanat 447 H wa-yadkhul fīhi takawwun al-ʻulūm al-Islāmīyah wa-naql al-ʻulūm al-dakhīlah ilá nuḍj al-ʻilm fī awāsiṭ al-qarn al-khāmis lil-Hijrah -- al-Juzʼ al-thālith. Yaḥtawī ʻalá tārīkh ādāb al-lughah al-ʻArabīyah min dukhūl al-Salājiqah Baghdād sanat 447 H ilá dukhūl al-Faransāwīyīn Miṣr sanat 1213 H, 1798 M wa-yadkhul fīhi thimār al-qarāʼiḥ wa-al-ʻuqūl fī al-ʻaṣr al-ʻAbbāsī al-rābiʻ wa-al-ʻaṣr al-Maghūlī, wa-al-ʻaṣr al-ʻUthmānī, wa-hiya akthar ʻuṣūr ādāb al-lughah nitājan wa-fīhā ẓaharat aham al-maʻājim wa-al-mawsūʻāt wa-awsaʻ kutub al-tārīkh wa-al-jughrāfiyah wa-al-lughah mimmā tudāwiluhu al-aydī --</subfield>
	</datafield>
